<paragraph blockId="13.[106,1096,274,390]" pageId="13" pageNumber="294">
The records of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="V. I. Gusarov" baseAuthorityName="Bernhauer" baseAuthorityYear="1903" box="[286,393,274,298]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="italica">
<emphasis box="[286,393,274,298]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="294">D. italica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the Cottian Alps (
<bibRefCitation author="LUIGIONI, P." box="[682,859,274,298]" pageId="13" pageNumber="294" pagination="1 - 1160" refId="ref10704" refString="LUIGIONI, P. 1929: I coleotteri d'Italia. Catalogo sinonimico-topografico-bibliografico. - Memorie della Pontificia Accademia delle Scienze (II) 13: 1 - 1160." type="journal article" year="1929">LUIGIONI 1929</bibRefCitation>
) and from northern 
<collectingCountry box="[106,156,305,329]" name="Italy" pageId="13" pageNumber="294">Italy</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="ZANETTI, A." box="[173,339,305,329]" pageId="13" pageNumber="294" pagination="1 - 65" refId="ref10789" refString="ZANETTI, A. 1995: Habrocerinae, Trichophyinae, Tachyporinae e Aleocharinae (generi 148 - 314), pp. 33 - 58. - In: CICERONI, A.; PUTHZ, V. &amp; ZANETTI, A.: Coleoptera, Polyphaga III (Staphylinidae). Checklist delle specie della fauna italiana. - Calderini Bologna, Fasc. 48: 1 - 65." type="book chapter" year="1995">ZANETTI 1995</bibRefCitation>
) may refer to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="PEYRON" baseAuthorityYear="1857" box="[499,631,305,329]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erichsoni">
<emphasis box="[499,631,305,329]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="294">D. erichsoni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, of which I have seen material only from southeastern 
<collectingCountry box="[254,329,336,359]" name="France" pageId="13" pageNumber="294">France</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="ASSING, V." box="[344,509,335,360]" pageId="13" pageNumber="294" pagination="111 - 149" refId="ref10580" refString="ASSING, V. 2005 b: On the western Palaearctic species of Drusilla LEACH, with special reference to the species of the eastern Mediterranean (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae, Aleocharinae). - Koleopterologische Rundschau 75: 111 - 149." type="journal article" year="2005">ASSING 2005b</bibRefCitation>
). The presence of this species in 
<collectingCountry box="[869,919,335,359]" name="Italy" pageId="13" pageNumber="294">Italy</collectingCountry>
is doubtful and requires verification.
</paragraph>
